<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Qudaıym, Seniń erkiń ҮРәж117</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
. Eb                   Bb7
 Qudaıym, Seniń erkiń bolsyn,
.                   Eb
 Ydysyń etshi meni Óziń.
.                Eb   Ab
 Erkimdi meniń qaıta qurshy,
.        Eb     Bb7    Eb
 Aldyńda Seniń senip turmyn.

[V2]
 Qudaıym, Seniń erkiń bolsyn,
 Teksershi, synap meni Óziń.
 Qardan da áppaq meni aǵartshy,
 Momyndyq bershi, sabyrly etshi.

[V3]
 Qudaıym, Seniń erkiń bolsyn,
 Aınala azap júrekti túıreıt.
 Kúsh penen bershi bekemdilik,
 Qutqar, aıashy, Patshasy álem.

[V4]
 Qudaıym, Seniń erkiń bolsyn,
 Adamdar bilsin ómir mánin.
 Júrek eselep Rýhty ańsaıdy:
 «Qudaıdy menen, - dep, - kórse árkim».</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
<hymn_number>117</hymn_number>
<author>George C. Stebbins, Adelaide A. Pollard</author>
</song>